# Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)

This license lets others distribute, remix, adapt, and build upon your work, even commercially, as long as they credit you for the original creation. This is the most flexible CC license in terms of what others can do with your works.

## Full License

You can view the full license at [Creative Commons](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/legalcode).

## Summary

- **Attribution**: You must give appropriate credit, provide a link to the license, and indicate if changes were made. You may do so in any reasonable manner, but not in any way that suggests the licensor endorses you or your use.
- **No additional restrictions**: You may not apply legal terms or technological measures that legally restrict others from doing anything the license permits.
